data.description: This 3/2/2 in Stuart on. .49 acre is brimming with unique character and undeniable charm, this beautiful home is a must-see treasure. Come bring your boats, motorcycles, RVs and other toys. With an hoa at only $27 a month, what are you waiting for? Boasting 3 bedrooms and 2 baths, this residence is equipped with a BRAND NEW Air Conditioner, ensuring your comfort year-round. The 8-year-old roof is one less thing you'll need to think about, while the recently renovated Primary Bathroom and NEWER appliances add a touch of contemporary elegance. Natural light floods through the windows, creating an inviting and warm ambiance throughout the home. The Florida Room, a versatile and delightful space, offers endless possibilities for relaxation or entertainment. It serves as a window to the picturesque outdoors, overlooking a lush, expansive yard adorned with mature trees - a serene retreat for any nature lover.
